THE SECRET SAUCE OF LIGHTHOUSE

Welcome to Lighthouse, your neighborhood spot in Williamsburg for nearly 13 years! Here, we believe in openness, transparency, and the power of community. Our farm-to-table menu is crafted with love, featuring seasonal dishes that are fresh, clean, and full of flavor.

ON SEASON

Lighthouse is dedicated to sustainability, both environmental and social. It prioritizes local, organic sourcing, minimizes waste, and supports regenerative agriculture. 

THE EXPERIENCE

ALWAYS FRESH

The Lighthouse menu highlights fresh, vibrant ingredients with a focus on bold, natural flavors. Featuring seasonal vegetables, sustainable seafood, and grass fed meats, each dish is crafted with quality and taste in mind. 

OUR PHILOSOPHY

COMMUNITY CENTERED

Lighthouse is grounded in its commitment to the community, actively engaging with and supporting local initiatives. The restaurant serves as a neighborhood hub, where food and hospitality bring people together. 

TABLE TALK

"Eating responsibly at Lighthouse BK"

Assaf and Naama Tamir, the proprietors of the Williamsburg restaurant, take scrupulous care to insure that their ingredients are ethically processed, offering Mediterranean meze and jerk-marinated chicken shawarma.

- The New Yorker

"Slow Food NYC To Honor Naama Tamir Of Lighthouse Restaurant With Snailblazer Award"

"With an unmatched commitment to restaurant sustainability and delicious cuisine, her dedication to community is an example of what it means to bring good, clean and fair food to all."

- prnewswire

"Lighthouse raised $30k for composter"

For the last 12 years, Lighthouse has always made you feel at home. The menu is seasonal, the food is ingredient driven, clean, fresh and delicious. Produce is locally sourced from farmers and growers the team loves.
